1_15de5wZ71q8iQGhEmBkJnRKx37Defn5XoL.body:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.mkg20001.zeronet

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.torproject.android

Start orbot 

Don't change proxy settings 

Start zeronet 

Turn on tor mode in zeronet 
Restart zeronet
Wait when tor service up
Enjoy

Just ignore. I tested, if orbot working, zeronet in tor mode works too. If shut down orbot, zeronet stops downloading and uploading, sorry for bad English 

Note: after restarting zeronet, wait when tor hidden service up
